        <h1>Magic Ball Keno</h1>

        <!-- GAME CANVAS -->
        <canvas id="kenoMagicBallCanvas" width="800" height="600"></canvas>

        <!-- GAME DESCRIPTION -->
        <div class="game-info">
          <h2>Magic Ball Keno</h2>
          <p>
            Magic Ball Keno is one of many Keno variants. Game is played on a
            smaller board, players pick 1–6 numbers from 1–36. After the draw of
            six numbers, one of the drawn numbers is randomly designated the
            magic ball. If the player has selected that magic number, their win
            is multiplied by 11, giving a big bonus on top of the normal payout.
            RTP is 95.76%
          </p>
        </div>

